title: EYL #167: How to Start a Business in 2022

description:
For the 3-year anniversary of EYL. We brought back our first-ever Alumni, Ms. Business. This is one of the most important episodes that we have recorded. The topic is “How to Start a Business”. Everything from filing, setting up the legal structure, tax deductions, business credit, and more. #business #credit #taxes
